    "headline": "Michelle Yeoh to join business and political leaders at Global Citizen NOW summit to fight poverty",
    "headline_extended": "Oscar winner Michelle Yeoh, Botswana President Mokgweetsi Masisi, and Verizon CEO Hans Vestberg are among the diverse group of political, business and philanthropic leaders Global Citizen will convene in New York on May 1 and 2, the nonprofit announced on Thursday",
